        <mxCell id="Un_F-MR6GsEnXFPlypb7-12" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;" value="FUNCTIONAL REQUIREMENTS&#xa;&#xa;• API Management (create, trigger, schedule APIs)&#xa;• API Health Monitoring (UP/DOWN detection)&#xa;• Broker Routing (Kafka, RabbitMQ, Redis)&#xa;• Event Publishing System&#xa;• Consumer Processing &amp; Logging&#xa;• Real-time Dashboard&#xa;• Fault Simulation (enable/disable consumers)&#xa;&#xa;" vertex="1">
